<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Certificate of Participation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .abstract-shapes {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
        }
        .shape {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            opacity: 0.6;
        }
        .shape:nth-child(1) { width: 150px; height: 150px; background: #4285F4; top: 10%; left: 5%; }
        .shape:nth-child(2) { width: 100px; height: 100px; background: #34A853; top: 30%; right: 10%; }
        .shape:nth-child(3) { width: 120px; height: 120px; background: #FBBC05; bottom: 20%; left: 15%; }
        .shape:nth-child(4) { width: 180px; height: 180px; background: #EA4335; bottom: 5%; right: 5%; }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 700px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            margin: auto;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .header img {
            width: 120px;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4285F4;
        }
        .content {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #333;
            margin-top: 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #EA4335;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 22px;
        }
        .event-title {
            color: #34A853;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .survey-link {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #1A73E8;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="abstract-shapes">
        <div class="shape"></div>
        <div class="shape"></div>
        <div class="shape"></div>
        <div class="shape"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://www.gdscnsut.com/Assets2/Images/DSC-Logo.png" alt="GDSC Logo">
            <div class="title">GDSC NSUT</div>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <span class="highlight">NAME_PLACEHOLDER</span>,</p>
            <p>We are pleased to present you with this certificate for successfully attending the event:</p>
            <p class="event-title">Fundamentals of Deep Learning and Its Application for Security</p>
            <p>Your participation and dedication are truly appreciated. We hope this event has provided you with valuable knowledge and insights.</p>
            <p>The certificate is attached to this email for your reference.</p>
            <p>We would love to hear your feedback! Please take a moment to fill out our survey:</p>
            <p class="survey-link"><a href="https://www.instagram.com/udaybhatia7" target="_blank">Click here to complete the survey</a></p>
            <p>Keep learning and keep growing!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            Regards, <br>
            <strong>Google Developer Student Clubs - NSUT</strong>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
